OL,3,CCoroner orders report on safety of
OL,4,Cbarriers at Wembley after Oasis fan's
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FA coroner has raised concerns over the
OL,8,Fsafety of barriers at Wembley Stadium
OL,9,Fafter the death of an Oasis fan who
OL,10,Ffell from height at one of the band's
OL,11,Fconcerts, a pre-inquest review heard.
OL,13,FLandscape gardener Lee Claydon, 45, of
OL,14,FBournemouth, Dorset, died following
OL,15,Fthe incident at the stadium in north-
OL,16,Fwest London on August 2 last year.
OL,18,FOn Thursday, senior coroner Andrew
OL,19,FWalker ordered a report looking into
OL,20,Fthe safety of barriers at the venue,
OL,21,FBarnet Coroner's Court heard.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/7
