CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1772358840
OL,3,CCoroner orders report on safety of
OL,4,Cbarriers at Wembley after Oasis fan's
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FHe said the report should review the
OL,8,Fdesign, height and placement of
OL,9,Fbarriers on level five of the stadium,
OL,10,Fwhere Mr Claydon fell from.
OL,12,FThe coroner said the report should
OL,13,Falso contain a risk assessment of the
OL,14,Fplacement of the barriers, and
OL,15,Findicate whether any modifications
OL,16,Fhave been made to the barriers since
OL,17,Ftheir installation, and whether safety
OL,18,Fregulations at the stadium provide "a
OL,19,Fsafe environment" for people attending
OL,20,Fthe venue.
OL,26,@zD@dOU{D@QO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/7
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
