OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1772358840
OL,3,CCoroner orders report on safety of
OL,4,Cbarriers at Wembley after Oasis fan's
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FMr Walker ordered the report in
OL,8,Fresponse to a letter received earlier
OL,9,Fthis year, understood to have been
OL,10,Fwritten by a former Wembley employee
OL,11,Fwho was working at the stadium around
OL,12,F20 years ago, which raised concerns
OL,13,Fover safety measures.
OL,15,FMr Walker said: "My concern is that
OL,16,Fthis area (the stadium) is safe and
OL,17,Fthat steps are taken as soon as
OL,18,Fpossible to make this area safe.
OL,26,@wD@QOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/7
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1772358840
OL,3,CCoroner orders report on safety of
OL,4,Cbarriers at Wembley after Oasis fan's
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,F"Although I am not an expert, this
OL,8,Freport (the letter) suggests that
OL,9,Fthere needs to be some steps taken to
OL,10,Fmake this area safe."
OL,12,FHe added: "What I really need to
OL,13,Funderstand is the risk associated with
OL,14,Fthe barriers."
OL,16,FThe letter, which was also seen by the
OL,17,FMetropolitan Police, was ordered by
OL,18,Fthe coroner to be disclosed to Brent
OL,19,FCouncil, Mr Claydon's family and the
OL,20,FFootball Association.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@UO]tD@KOUvD@NO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/7
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1772358840
OL,3,CCoroner orders report on safety of
OL,4,Cbarriers at Wembley after Oasis fan's
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FThe inquest was adjourned until
OL,8,Fanother pre-inquest review hearing on
OL,9,FApril 29 at the same court.
OL,11,FThe Met Police completed their
OL,12,Finvestigation into the gardener's
OL,13,Fdeath in November last year, ruling
OL,14,Fout the possibility of suicide or
OL,15,Fthird-party involvement, saying Mr
OL,16,FClaydon's death was a "tragic
OL,17,Faccident".
OL,19,FThe force added it had seen a
OL,20,Ftoxicology report and there were "no
OL,21,Fconcerns there".
OL,26,@xD@WOUyD@IO]|D@bOU}D@OO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/7
