CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1772358840
OL,3,CCoroner orders report on safety of
OL,4,Cbarriers at Wembley after Oasis fan's
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FMr Claydon's inquest opening, which
OL,8,Ftook place in September last year,
OL,9,Fheard the Oasis fan was taken to a
OL,10,Fmedical centre in Wembley after the
OL,11,Ffall, where he was pronounced dead at
OL,12,F10.38pm.
OL,14,FA post-mortem examination on August 6
OL,15,Flast year gave the preliminary medical
OL,16,Fcause of death as "multiple bodily
OL,17,Finjuries".
OL,26,@xD@SOUyD@IO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/7
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
