OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1772358840
OL,3,CCoroner orders report on safety of
OL,4,Cbarriers at Wembley after Oasis fan's
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FThe fall happened during a run of
OL,8,Fstadium shows for the rock band's sell-
OL,9,Fout Live '25 reunion tour ` their
OL,10,Ffirst since splitting in 2009.
OL,12,FOasis had previously said in a
OL,13,Fstatement: "We are shocked and
OL,14,Fsaddened to hear of the tragic death
OL,15,Fof a fan at the show.
OL,17,F"Oasis would like to extend our
OL,18,Fsincere condolences to the family and
OL,19,Ffriends of the person involved."
OL,26,@uD@LOUyD@AOU{D@`O]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/7
